data.description: Welcome to this cute home in the Hollybrook neighborhood of West Chico! This neighborhood has mature landscaping to enjoy and a community park/picnic area. And if being outdoors is your thing, wait until you see the large backyard! The home has 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath, with a sink and vanity area in the Primary bedroom. This home is close to schools, CSU Chico, Enloe Hospital, restaurants and grocery stores. With a newer roof and HVAC, this home is ready for you to come make it yours!
